gst-plugins-base: gst-plugins-base (GStreamer Base Plugins)
gst-plugins-base:
gst-plugins-base: This package contains a set of reference plugins, base classes for 
gst-plugins-base: other plugins, and helper libraries. This module is kept up-to-date 
gst-plugins-base: together with the core developments. This module contains elements for:
gst-plugins-base:    * device plugins: x(v)imagesink, alsa, v4lsrc, cdparanoia
gst-plugins-base:    * codecs: vorbis, theora
gst-plugins-base:    * network: tcp
gst-plugins-base:    * audio processing: audioconvert, adder, audiorate, audioscale, volume
gst-plugins-base:    * visualisation: libvisual
gst-plugins-base:    * video processing: ffmpegcolorspace
